age expenses within allotted marketing budget.Provide excellent customer services to ensure customer satisfaction and retention.Other duties as assigned.&nbsp; Apply at https://ngcareers.com/job/2019-06/channel-distribution-development-officer-fmcg-at-invent-alliance-limited-409/ Source: NG Career